title: Curious George the Movie (for iPod)
description:
The Curious George movie encoded and resized and tagged for an ipod.

Resolution: 432X232
Video Bit Rate: 640 kbps
Audio Bit Rate: 128 kbps
codec: h.264

Looks great on an ipod and pretty good on a full sized TV.  I keep movies my kids like in similar formats to this so they can watch it on our TV or take it on trips on the ipod and it doesn&#039;t take up too much space on the ipod&#039;s drive.
